                  </hi>. I live at 8, Oxford Terrace, Upper Holloway—I have been attending Mr. McCarthy, 22, Sussex Road North—I have seen him this morning; he is suffering from rheumatic gout; he cannot move out of his bed—he is not in a condition to come to this Court and be examined as a witness; it is physically impossible. (<hi rend="italic">The deposition of Francis McCarthy was put in and read.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
